title: Pennsylvania Fish and Boat Commission, PFBC Properties, Pennsylvania, 2005
name: Pennsylvania Fish and Boat Commission, PFBC Properties, Pennsylvania, 2005
description:
Abstract:

The Pennsylvania Fish and Boat Commission owns numerous properties across Pennsylvania.  This GIS layer contains point locations on each property.

Purpose:

Production of maps depicting where the Pennsylvania Fish and Boat Commission owns property. Also will be used to track projects/activties on properties and the tracking/assessment of conditions.

Supplemental_Information:

This data set was created by collecting coordinate locations using uncorrected handheld GPS techniques.  The coordinates were compiled in a spreadsheet and then a GIS layer was developed from the coordinates using ArcMap.
